name: Softly, as in a Morning Sunrise
Impressions
comments: Recorded live at the 'Village Vanguard' jazz club in Greenwich Village, New York City. This was the first released recording of "Impressions" by Coltrane. Two earlier recordings from November 1 and 3, 1961, were released in 1979 on "The Mastery of John Coltrane, Vol. 4 - Trane's Moods", Impulse!, catalog IZ 9361-2. The earliest recording of "Impressions" is from Coltrane's appearance on July 1, 1961 at the Newport Jazz Festival; however, this version has never been officially released.
